resource.http://dev.llgc.org.uk/sas/full_text: University of Canterbury catalogue stamp. The Lübeck was catalogued, as were many of the 'old and special books', in 1969. It is known from various articles that this item was at Canterbury College/University well before this stamp indicates. Today the Lübeck is part of the Rare Books collection located in the Macmillan Brown Library, University of Canterbury.
resource.chars:
University of Canterbury catalogue stamp. 

The Lübeck was catalogued, as were many of the 'old and special books', in 1969. It is known from various articles that this item was at Canterbury College/University well before this stamp indicates. Today the Lübeck is part of the Rare Books collection located in the Macmillan Brown Library, University of Canterbury.
